Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.47,0:02:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,How many did you eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.98,0:02:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Seventeen.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.19,0:02:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,No, eighteen.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.36,0:02:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,No, maybe nineteen?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.65,0:02:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,And how many are left?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.28,0:02:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.90,0:02:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.86,0:02:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You {\i1}already{\i0} know!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.16,0:02:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.66,0:02:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Eight...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.49,0:02:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Eight?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.49,0:02:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Eighty-one!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.71,0:02:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be fine if I just eat them all, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.16,0:02:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think you'll be able to eat all of them?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.96,0:02:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.00,0:02:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Holo, the wise wolf of Yoitz!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.67,0:02:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't need to be so obstinate.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.47,0:02:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Who's{\i0} obstinate?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.43,0:02:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the real truth?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.93,0:02:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It {\i1}is{\i0} the real truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.39,0:02:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the {\i1}real{\i0} real truth?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.97,0:02:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the real real truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.73,0:02:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the real, real, real truth?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.85,0:02:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the real, real, real truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.90,0:02:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, I'm getting sick of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.03,0:02:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd imagine so.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.78,0:03:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if they're your favorite food, you had twenty yesterday and almost as many today.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.37,0:03:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.16,0:03:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'll show you I can eat them all!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.54,0:03:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to be so stubborn about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.71,0:03:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You may be tired of the raw fruit,\Nbut there are lots of other ways to eat apples.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.68,0:03:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Other ways? What other ways?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.56,0:03:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Don't ridicule me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.27,0:03:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never heard of apples being baked before!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.98,0:03:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You've seriously never eaten apple pie?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.15,0:03:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Such a thing really exists?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.15,0:03:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you bake it in a pan with dough.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.11,0:03:47.41,Default,,0,0,0,,And if you do that, it becomes chewy...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.41,0:03:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't a good example,\Nbut it's as if they started rotting.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.04,0:03:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But just like things taste good right before they go bad, baked apples are extremely tasty, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.00,0:04:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,When you eat fresh apples, they moisten your dry throat.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.01,0:04:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,But baked apples are so sweet that they make your throat dry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.47,0:04:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm sure you're tired of sweet food.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.06,0:04:13.77,Default,,0,0,0,,So, we'll have a change of pace for dinner and have salted meat or fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.77,0:04:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Which would you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.60,0:04:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Meat!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.69,0:04:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to that girl who looked\Nlike she couldn't eat any more?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.86,0:04:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,If it is meat, it's a different story.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.57,0:04:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.20,0:04:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, don't forget that you need to take care of these apples.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.28,0:04:29.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.33,0:04:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I have confidence I can eat them all after what I just heard!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.21,0:04:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I have some business too, so let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.00,0:04:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.55,0:04:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm treating you to a change in mood so you won't get sick of me.{I changed my mood to keep you from getting tired of me. (In reference obviously to her sudden change of mood a moment ago)}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.22,0:04:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,When I swallow your treats whole, I tend to get heartburn.{You're inedible. ("inedible"/kuuenai means something like "someone you can't let your guard down with because they're clever/sly")}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.85,0:04:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want me to tell you that was clever?{(Referring to the fact that Lawrence's last line is a pun, since Holo's line had been an extention of them talking about her being tired of eating apples)}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.56,0:04:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.73,0:05:01.73,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.9\fscx105\fs80\fnMailart Rubberstamp\c&H7A8995&\pos(640,458)}Wolf and the Tail of Happiness
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.23,0:05:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.87,0:05:11.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.41,0:05:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,How should I say it? You...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.01,0:05:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You really do look like a nun.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.47,0:05:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed. It's convenient for traveling, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.56,0:05:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.27,0:05:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,People are as strange as ever, treating each other so differently
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.12,0:05:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,based on whether they're wearing a specific piece of cloth or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.06,0:05:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,There are times when it's convenient\Nfor wolves to wear sheep's clothing too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.90,0:05:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.11,0:05:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,If I wore rabbit's fur, I'm sure you'd fall into my trap instantly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.53,0:05:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I guess I should carry some apples as protection in case I get caught.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.41,0:05:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Just when I finally forgot about apples...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.50,0:06:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.21,0:06:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,,In your case, looking too much\Nlike a nun could lead to problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.97,0:06:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Like what?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.26,0:06:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Nuns don't drink during the day under any circumstances.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.56,0:06:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,That just makes me an amazing nun, right?{i must be a hella radical nun, yeah?}{any suggestions?}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.98,0:06:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,And nuns don't talk like that, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.44,0:06:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I beg your pardon, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.69,0:06:27.74,Default,,1,1,0,,In all seriousness, there will be places where dressing as a nun would be a bad idea once we head north.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.41,0:06:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,So what should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.03,0:06:32.45,Default,,0,0,0,,So, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.08,0:06:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it'd make things safer for you\Nto have a set of clothes like a city girl's.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.04,0:06:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go and buy some before we eat, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.80,0:06:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,If our minds are on business,\Nour meal won't be as good.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.60,0:06:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-Thank you. I'm glad I don't have to try and persuade you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.14,0:06:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Were you thinking I'd say we should eat and drink first?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.14,0:06:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't get distracted by food that easily!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.85,0:06:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.19,0:07:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I can hardly hamper your attempts to look out for my feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.32,0:07:11.99,Default,,1,1,0,,Did you really think I wouldn't notice after you came up with\Nsuch a grand, important reason just to buy me some clothes?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.24,0:07:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'll cast aside my sheepishness and let you buy them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.45,0:07:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It's going to be a cold, cold winter, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.08,0:07:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you don't have to cast it all aside.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.29,0:07:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.63,0:07:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no money.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.84,0:07:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.26,0:07:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not what I meant.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.43,0:07:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm saying I don't have small change.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.43,0:07:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Better too big than too small, as they say.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.68,0:07:39.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You can simply use that money, no?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.69,0:07:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,There's also the saying about skinning a rabbit with a meat cleaver.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.06,0:07:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,If I used this money at a clothing store,\NI can't imagine how annoyed they'd be.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.86,0:07:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.15,0:07:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,,But are gold coins really worth so much?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.74,0:07:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.28,0:07:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,For example, a Lumione gold coin is currently worth thirty-five Trenni silver coins.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.24,0:08:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,If you live humbly, one silver coin can last seven days.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.67,0:08:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's worth thirty-five times that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.71,0:08:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,That's quite something.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.59,0:08:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.71,0:08:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The store said that these clothes were worth two gold coins.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.46,0:08:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Unlike apples, wouldn't clothes\Nbe something you'd buy with gold coins?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.55,0:08:19.31,Default,,0,0,0,,If that were true, most of the people in the city would be naked.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.31,0:08:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure the merchant who sold those clothes\Nmust've been quite worried that you'd even pay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.10,0:08:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Were these that expensive?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.27,0:08:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.69,0:08:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,So choose some shabby-looking clothes when we buy them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.40,0:08:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Holo, the wise wolf of Yoitz!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.91,0:08:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,If I wear something shabby, it'll tarnish my name!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.08,0:08:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,They say that if you are truly beautiful,\Nthen anything should look good on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.46,0:08:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose the money exchange is the next—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.96,0:08:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, we're going to exchange money?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.75,0:08:48.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we're going to that bridge, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.01,0:08:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.55,0:08:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up and walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.51,0:08:56.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to go drinking soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.14,0:09:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Lumione, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.85,0:09:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Today's market price for it\Nis thirty-four Trenni silver coins on the dot.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.23,0:09:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And the handling charge?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.61,0:09:12.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Ten Lute coins, or thirty Trie coins.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.82,0:09:15.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll pay in Lute coins.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.91,0:09:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood. Well then...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.95,0:09:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, please be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.95,0:09:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,If you drop them, they'll belong to whoever picks them up off the street.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.00,0:09:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Weiz.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.79,0:09:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.46,0:09:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the customer.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.51,0:09:36.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave the gold coin there. I'm busy right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.22,0:09:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though you're not even treating your precious customers properly?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.05,0:09:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.76,0:09:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It's more important that this precious little lady doesn't drop any coins.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.23,0:09:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.66,0:09:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,My, that makes me happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.48,0:09:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,But, dear sir...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.15,0:09:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.69,0:09:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,There are just too many coins for my hand to hold.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.28,0:10:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why my hands are there, {*}Miss Holo{*Holo-san}.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.70,0:10:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,My, but we can't do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.04,0:10:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't be able to use your precious hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.50,0:10:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Not at all! I'll gladly use my hands so that these coins won't fall from your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.00,0:10:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It does not trouble me in any way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.55,0:10:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That is because my chest burns for you with a fire that I cannot bear myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.30,0:10:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,and I know that you'll help me bear it in turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.43,0:10:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Weiz!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.10,0:10:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you forget the basics of being a money exchanger?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.27,0:10:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Silver in a bag, gold in a chest.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.48,0:10:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Only crude copper coins should be kept in hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.90,0:10:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.57,0:10:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Keeping such a good girl to yourself is an act against God.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.32,0:10:41.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Haven't you heard the passage that says to share what bread you can offer?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.07,0:10:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You want me to share?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.53,0:10:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no lending at the money exchange table.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.71,0:10:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Only a full exchange or no exchange.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.54,0:10:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,If you take her, the debt she\Nowes me comes with her,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.38,0:10:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,so you need to show\Nme you're ready for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.71,0:11:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't possibly place a price on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.26,0:11:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Just how can you say that, you corrupt merchant!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.39,0:11:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,The scale in my heart is still tilting back and forth right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.56,0:11:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,But please, believe that it is not tilting because of the weight of gold coins.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.57,0:11:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course! Of course, I believe you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.11,0:11:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You really are a wicked man{i checked},\Nto touch a tilting scale with your hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.75,0:11:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{*}Miss Holo{*Holo-san}...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.25,0:11:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, let's get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.42,0:11:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey, Lawrence.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.21,0:11:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You came to exchange some gold coins,\Nso are you going shopping or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.76,0:11:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.88,0:11:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Prices seem like they're going to rise.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.59,0:11:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,So the faster, the better.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.19,0:11:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.72,0:11:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Do money exchangers work even when the sun sets?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.14,0:11:57.86,Default,,1,1,0,,Heaven forbid! You can be sure that money exchangers who use scales after the sun sets are swindlers!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.86,0:12:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And of course, I'm no swindler.{scamster}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.36,0:12:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You heard him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.32,0:12:04.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Once I buy clothes, I'll be going to the tavern early.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.99,0:12:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You can come if you want when you're done working.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.16,0:12:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, my brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.74,0:12:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the usual tavern, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.04,0:12:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It's scary to get drunk in a tavern you don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.96,0:12:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.09,0:12:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Right away! I'll really be there soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.68,0:12:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,That was as fun as I thought it'd be.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.01,0:12:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll regret it later if you get him too serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.12,0:12:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Regret it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.23,0:12:33.89,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll follow you around.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.89,0:12:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You're already following me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.06,0:12:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Unlike you, he knows he is playing a game.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.03,0:12:42.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fun teasing you,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.19,0:12:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,but I want to play with some smart males sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.45,0:12:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Both of us know that it's a game,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.20,0:12:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,so could you not act so serious about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.04,0:12:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll start blushing, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.53,0:13:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, although that Weiz fellow is more of an eloquent talker than you,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.84,0:13:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{I've lived for a long time,}{but I've never met anyone like him, whose words I cannot trust at all.}{I made dozens of these kinds of changes when I was working on the original release in 2017. Which translation was correct? the one on the left (sudo)? the one on the right (LN)? I can make my best guess, but I'm just glad you're on this project now.}I've lived long enough to know that nothing is so untrustworthy as the words we say.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.88,0:13:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure a man of business like yourself would understand that to some degree.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.93,0:13:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I'd tell any lie as long as it brought me profit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.69,0:13:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,They won't work on me, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.44,0:13:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, let's go shopping for clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.69,0:13:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.99,0:13:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You've twice missed your chance to grasp the happiness God granted.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.41,0:13:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't grasp it next time,\Nthe tail of happiness might escape you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.33,0:13:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.33,0:13:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Holo! Wait for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.68,0:13:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,That one right there is forty Lute.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.51,0:13:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It's quite durable for that price.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.52,0:14:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm heading north, so could you find some things that'll be cheap and warm for the two of us?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.53,0:14:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What is your budget?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.24,0:14:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Two Trenni coins.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.91,0:14:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Please leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.28,0:14:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,A set of robes, two blankets...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.04,0:14:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,And would something like this be fine?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.75,0:14:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.38,0:14:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,As you can see, I'm a merchant.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.92,0:14:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,On my travels, I became friends with the Milone Company here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.63,0:14:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? With Milone?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.80,0:14:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, so I might stop by a few times a year from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.39,0:14:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.27,0:14:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Then let me add another blanket along with this robe.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.11,0:14:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, they've been smoked,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.40,0:14:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,so I guarantee that they'll repel bugs for two years.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.33,0:15:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't we come to buy clothes for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.96,0:15:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.17,0:15:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you telling me to wear that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.09,0:15:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to try and fight the cold off with that robe alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.18,0:15:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,If you are upset about my spending your\Nmoney without asking, just say so.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.81,0:15:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Holo, the wise wolf.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.48,0:15:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm smart and I have good business sense, but my nose is sharp too!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.02,0:15:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,The day I wear that, my nose will turn up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.61,0:15:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought having you suffer a bit\Nmight fix that twisted personality of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.24,0:15:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't get angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.78,0:15:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll let you in on the secret later.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.16,0:15:37.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.87,0:15:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.70,0:15:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have any nice clothes for women?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.46,0:15:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Clothes for women?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.21,0:15:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Something that won't cause much trouble in northern cities,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.71,0:15:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,in about her size.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.89,0:15:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well. Please wait just a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.01,0:15:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,How about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.02,0:16:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a court attendant's dress that was bought from another shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.90,0:16:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want something that gaudy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.86,0:16:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't suit you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.27,0:16:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I want something simpler and easy to change into.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.75,0:16:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.62,0:16:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir, how about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.62,0:16:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.91,0:16:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.96,0:16:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You're quite the person to have laid your eyes on this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.71,0:16:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,These articles were once worn by a noble.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.59,0:16:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Just look. The seams are sewn neatly, and it won't tear so easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.76,0:16:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What you should really be looking at is this walnut-colored cap.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.39,0:16:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Once you wear this over your shoulder
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.52,0:16:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,and wear this specially tailored triangular cap just like the servants at this noble's house,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.52,0:16:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,you'll become the most envied girl in town just like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.57,0:16:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,A rabbit?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.90,0:16:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Does it make you hungry?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.32,0:16:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.53,0:16:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,How much is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.53,0:17:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,For the two of them, let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.16,0:17:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Ten Trenni coins.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.79,0:17:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,,No, how about nine coins?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.46,0:17:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.79,0:17:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,In deference to the beautiful lady here, I'll make it eight coins.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.97,0:17:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.84,0:17:20.72,Default,,1,1,0,,If someone as cute as myself would show them off for all to see right here and now, would you make it seven coins?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.14,0:17:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,V-Very well, I'll let you have it for seven coins.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.94,0:17:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.98,0:17:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me then.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.04,0:17:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.79,0:17:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.12,0:17:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Paying one Trenni for this was a steal!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.75,0:17:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Were these clothes too expensive?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.51,0:17:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,No, seven coins for those is quite good.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.85,0:18:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You still had enough confidence to drive the price down?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.98,0:18:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought if I picked the kind of clothes you are carrying,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.60,0:18:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,we could have purchased them for one\Ntenth of the price we paid for these.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.73,0:18:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.82,0:18:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I actually thought it would've cost more, so don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.82,0:18:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.86,0:18:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as you temper your drinking later,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.07,0:18:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,you'll make up for the seven coins right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.28,0:18:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't drink that much!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.96,0:18:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,But still, the way you bargained with him was really cheap.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.46,0:18:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how expert the\Nmerchant is, he can't beat that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.46,0:18:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,All males are idiots, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.93,0:18:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you going to do with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.64,0:18:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Taking it with you to the tavern?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.76,0:18:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,No, not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.98,0:18:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,But the inn isn't this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.23,0:18:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I won't be leaving it at the inn either.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.52,0:18:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to sell these at a different clothes shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.11,0:18:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,We can buy some clothes for the cold when we head a bit further north.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.32,0:19:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to sell them?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.74,0:19:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no point in keeping them\Nif we're not going to use them, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.66,0:19:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true, but will they sell high?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.25,0:19:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.83,0:19:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Seeing a profit would be difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.04,0:19:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll probably have a bit of a loss.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.17,0:19:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You're still going to sell them if you have a loss?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.88,0:19:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't understand why?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.17,0:19:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on, I'm thinking now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.60,0:19:31.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Shall I tell you the secret?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.98,0:19:34.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't ask you to tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.27,0:19:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,But if you want to say it, then go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.24,0:19:42.95,Default,,0,0,0,,That said, it's nothing special,\Nand you did a better job after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.91,0:19:46.29,Default,,0,0,0,,This bunch of clothes is worth two coins.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.29,0:19:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,For example, let's say we sell these\Nat a different store for half the price.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.08,0:19:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd have a loss of one coin.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.92,0:19:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.00,0:19:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But let's direct our attention to something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.55,0:19:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Something else?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.38,0:19:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.30,0:20:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyone can tell at a glance that your robe is high grade, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.26,0:20:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,My robe...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.72,0:20:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It's safe to say that a person wearing it wouldn't ever go to a shop like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.77,0:20:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,So that shop owner wanted to have a good relationship with me since I was with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.36,0:20:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Now then, if you were him, what would you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.15,0:20:20.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd sell things cheap to leave a good impression.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.49,0:20:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.82,0:20:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And what follows from that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.41,0:20:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,That owner lowered the price on these a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.33,0:20:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Then he lowered the price on yours a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.58,0:20:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,We were the customers who'd taken two coins worth of these ragged clothes off his hands after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.34,0:20:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,However, there's a huge gap between the two prices.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.53,0:20:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,And what does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.97,0:20:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,If we think about the total balance, we saved a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.60,0:20:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Well done.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.14,0:20:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What a cheap trick. A completely cheap trick!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.02,0:20:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That trick?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.36,0:20:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.32,0:21:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm amazed you even thought of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.74,0:21:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,That's called business sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.24,0:21:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Though your brute force technique was better in the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.03,0:21:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Naturally.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.62,0:21:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Your shallow thinking can't beat my scheming.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.08,0:21:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You've said it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.25,0:21:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You think you can win?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.75,0:21:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, if you're confident about it,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.84,0:21:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,maybe you could show me your skills when we go drinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.17,0:21:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,When we go drinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.76,0:21:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Make sure you pay a high price for me, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.43,0:21:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'll buy you, all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.81,0:21:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,But the payment will be in apples.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.18,0:21:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You're pretty tough, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.98,0:21:37.27,Default,TLC,0,0,0,,If you bake me, I might become a bit sweeter.{i don't really know what to do with any of this}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.52,0:21:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You're pretty well baked already.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.73,0:21:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Males baked with jealousy are too sweet to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.90,0:21:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What about you, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.49,0:21:47.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to have a bite and see for yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.16,0:21:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.38,0:22:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You grasped it properly the third time.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.49,0:23:45.00,Default,,0,0,15,,{\i1}Next Episode: "Wolf and a Proper Balance."
